Jacks_Ice_Sword.help: Jack can summon a Ice Sword that deals above average damage and can Slow foes' attack speed.
Jacks_Ice_Sword.targetHelp: Jack's Ice Sword has reduced your attack rate.

Jacks_Ice_Bolt.help: Ice Bolt quickly pelts an enemy with small icy daggers; their chill Slows a foe's attacks and movement for a time. Fast, but little damage. Damage: Minor, Recharge: Fast
Jacks_Ice_Bolt.targetHelp: Jack's Ice Bolt has reduced your Attack rate and Running speed.

Jacks_Freezing_Touch.help: This Freezing Touch will encase a single foe in a block of ice. This will deal high damage over time, as well as freezing them in their tracks, leaving them cold and helpless. Damage: High(DoT), Recharge: Slow
Jacks_Freezing_Touch.targetHelp: Jack's Freezing Touch has frozen you solid.

Jacks_Greater_Ice_Sword.help: Summons a more powerful and deadly Ice Sword. Like Ice Sword, Greater Ice Sword can slow your foes' attack speed.
Jacks_Greater_Ice_Sword.targetHelp: Jack's Ice Sword has reduced your attack rate.

Chilling_Embrace.help: While active, you dramatically lower the temperature around yourself, Slowing the attack rate of all nearby foes, as well as their movement speed. Recharge: Very Fast
Chilling_Embrace.targetHelp: Your Attack speed and Running speed are reduced by the Chilling Embrace.

Resistance.help: Jack takes little damage from Cold attacks. Jack is also resistant to Sleep and Disorient.
